          }
        },
        "rich_text_ih8f7U": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lab Grown Diamond Jewelry is redefining luxury with its elegance, and meaningful impact. People today are moving beyond just gifting items, they’re investing in meaningful experiences to celebrate milestones and special moments. There’s a cultural shift happening globally. The focus is on living in the present and amplifying that joy in unforgettable ways. Following this trend, luxury gifting is on the rise. Luxury is no longer related to exclusivity of origin, but to exclusivity in design. Sustainability and ethics are becoming an integral part of the DNA of the new age luxury market as the thoughts of customers emphasize the need for environmental conservation. </p><p>Lab Grown Diamond jewelry is stealing the spotlight as they are sustainable, brilliant and visibly luxurious. New brands in the industry are enhancing the feel of luxury with thoughtfulness in every element - craftsmanship,more personalization options, packaging and post sales service that ensures that the jewelry looks classy throughout generations.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_tt3fKf": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Lab Grown Diamonds Are The Future",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Lab Grown Diamonds Are The Future</h2>",
            "custom_id": "future"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_wVdLn8": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sustainable_Necklace.jpg",
            "text": "<p>From Meghan Markle to Taylor Swift, celebrities are boldly choosing luxury that comes with no guilt. Not just them as flag bearers, the GenZ and Millennials are gaining more knowledge about Lab Grown Diamonds and hence, are not easily swayed by myths. Lab Grown Diamonds are the same as natural diamonds optically and scientifically. Crafted in controllable environments, they are flawless and typically cost less than Natural Diamonds. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kTFXEm": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lab Grown Diamonds also are redefining the 4C’s with enhanced beauty with even more colors to choose from.  At Lucira Jewelry, we have introduced exclusive cuts and collections to add to the numerous perks of buying Lab Grown Diamond Jewelry.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bKUrCM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Lab Grown Diamond Necklace Sets are Perfect For Luxury Gifting",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Lab Grown Diamond Necklace Sets are Perfect For Luxury Gifting</h2>",
            "custom_id": "luxurygifting"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_RmtHdb": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Packaging_V3.png",
            "text": "<p>Women bring brilliance to the everyday and they deserve jewelry that reflects that same sparkle. Lucira Jewelry’s Lab Grown Diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-necklaces\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Necklace</span></a> sets are thoughtfully designed to complement both personal and professional moments. With their versatile elegance, these sets transition seamlessly from boardroom to celebration.</p><p>Each necklace set is beautifully packaged, making it the perfect choice for a meaningful gift -  whether for yourself, a loved one, or someone you deeply admire. They’re ideal for expressing gratitude, love, or appreciation with a touch of prestige.</p><p>You can even create a custom set by pairing coordinated pieces like a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/marquise-pear-cut-diamond-necklace\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Marquise and Pear Cut Diamond Necklace</span></a> with matching <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Earrings</span></a> and a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/cuff-bracelets\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Cuff Bracelet</span></a>. The result is a cohesive, minimal, and modern look that feels premium and personal.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qWN9jc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lab Grown Diamond Bridal Necklace Set",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lab Grown Diamond Bridal Necklace Set</h2>",
            "custom_id": "bridalset"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_fwe8Nr": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Mangalsutra_V3.png",
            "text": "<p>Gone are the days when brides wore only simple, traditional mangalsutras. Today’s bride is bold, elegant, and expressive. Whether you're looking for a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/gifts-for-wife\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">gift for wife</span></a> or a gift for your  fiancée, a bridal necklace set is more than a gift. It’s a precious gift that she’ll treasure forever.</p><p>Lucira Jewelry’s <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/mangalsutra-necklaces\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">mangalsutra necklaces</span></a> are designed for the modern woman - blending comfort, style, and luxury with every detail. Each piece is adorned with sparkling gemstones, mirroring the light she brings into your life.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_T39J9G": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If you're looking to gift something more aligned with her unique style, consider a layered diamond necklace paired with statement earrings, a set that's not just perfect for the wedding day but destined to become her signature look long after.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_wBKw73": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Not Just A Trend, A Cultural Shift ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Not Just A Trend, A Cultural Shift </h2><p>While necklace sets don’t only create a lasting impression, they are also not just a recent trend. There is a cultural shift in mindset as more people are looking for wearable gifts. Investments in luxury are increasing for various reasons - rewarding yourself with something you like, celebrating milestones with meaning, or simply investing on wearables with emotional value. </p><p>A De Beers Report says that over 80% of luxury jewelry purchases are tied to emotional purchases such as milestone moments, anniversaries, and self rewards. Likewise, a Bain and Company study says that 60% of consumers globally are buying jewelry and accessories to gift themselves, not just to others. </p>",
            "custom_id": "culturalshift"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_4Yyeyh": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Luxury Gifting with Lucira Jewelry: From Thoughtful to Timeless",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Luxury Gifting with Lucira Jewelry: From Thoughtful to Timeless</h2><p>Gifting is no longer about the price tag, but about the purpose and the meaning behind the gift. At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a>, we are honoured to be part of something so personal and don’t take this responsibility lightly. Our craftsmanship focuses on thoughtfully creating timeless pieces by blending traditional elegance with a contemporary twist. Our vast collection of <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-necklaces\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">tennis necklaces</span></a>, pendant necklaces, sui dhaga earrings, statement earrings and solitaire studs with customization displays that we have something unique for every woman. With diamonds so brilliant, craftsmanship so delicately intricate, and service so centered on maximizing comfort and joy, Lucira jewelry is designed to be the perfect luxury gift that you can choose from.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "luciragifting"
          }
        }
